task.summary: Default task
Convert all key values in ManageCategories and ManageFields to strings.
Insert MainWindow layouts into a dict and optimize init_layout method.
Set the modality to true for all classes except MainWindow.
Change 'header_title' to 'header' and 'header_logo' to 'logo' in MainWindow.
Fix a bug where keys in AddItem are integers instead of strings.
Initialize the first row in ManageFields when there are no fields.
Prevent the first row from being removed in ManageFields.
Fix a bug where the first row in ManageFields isn't initialized when the window opens without data a second time.
Change all instances of 'Media' to 'Category' in MainWindow.
Replace all instances of 'Title' with the appropriate user-created category ID in MainWindow.
Remove the internal 'Category' field from each record's unique ID.
Change the formatting of the internal 'Date Entered' field.
Remove the now defunct 'Status' label from the list of labels not to display when showing record data.
Add separators before and after categories in ManageCategories.
Add shadows to each separator in ManageCategories.
Remove horizontal margins from all layouts in ManageCategories.
Rework init_layout method code in ManageCategories.
Display a minimum of four category fields in ManageCategories.
Add separators before and after fields in ManageFields.
Display a minimum of seven fields in ManageFields.
Adjust button size and widget spacing in ManageCategories and ManageFields.
Reduce the number of default fields displayed in ManageFields by one.
Add a confirmation dialog that prompts the user to confirm that they want to quit the program when the 'Quit' button is pressed.
Implement the functionality for the 'Remove' button in MainWindow.
Add a confirmation dialog that is displayed when the 'Save' action is successful.
Store the file name of a catalog when it is exported.
If a current file doesn't exist when pressing the 'Save' button, export the catalog instead.
Add a method to MainWindow that loads the last used catalog from the previous session when the program starts and a method that saves the current catalog's address to a text file on exit.
Remove the outdated 'test-files' and 'list-item-icons' folders from the project.
Remove and replace outdated code in MainWindow that sets the icon for each list item.
Display the top item in the list of catalog items by default.
Change a catalog item's color to white while it is selected.
Remove code from ManageFields pertaining to a category ID.
Switch from dynamic to manual resizing of the ManageCategories frame.
Switch from dynamic to manual resizing of the ManageFields frame.
Switch from dynamic to manual positioning of the ManageFields frame.
Switch from dynamic to manual positioning of the ManageCategories frame.
Add a message to AddItem when a category is selected that doesn't have any fields.
Fix a bug where the program would crash when trying to add a record from a category that doesn't have any fields.
Add widgets to AddItem for selecting and displaying an optional image.
Overhaul the AddItem window's design.
Put category field labels on their own row in AddItem.
Fix a bug where the whitespace isn't removed from each string of field combo items.
Disable the 'Search' and 'Edit' buttons in MainWindow.
Move the 'Category' and 'Date Entered' field assignments for an item from MainWindow to AddItem.
Implement saving an item's image to the program directory when adding a new item.
Omit the 'Image Path' field when showing item details in MainWindow.
Remove the unused 'self.image' variable from AddItem.
When selected, display an item's image in the item details area in MainWindow.
